review.description: ok I love Mexican food but this is ridiculous !!!! 2 tacos and soda $10???? I am still Hungry!!! Man this is not the spot
review.author: Orlando R.

review.description: Love the location and it's fast and cheap! I feel like they could up the freshness of their ingredients: meat and all.
review.author: Stacie K.

review.description: Food was good and came out quick. Staff was happy to accommodate to special requests and friendly. This nice place to get a good burrito or tacos. Have to try the homemade red sauce, it is spicy but full of flavor. Small place but it has enough space for a decent sized group. I will come back again for the red sauce and the very fresh taste.
review.author: Derek M.
